パッケージの使用
manhattan.waveformdata

  • manhattan.waveformdataを使用しているパッケージ 
    パッケージ 説明
    manhattan.inversion  
    manhattan.waveformdata  
  • manhattan.inversionにより使用されるmanhattan.waveformdataのクラス 
    クラスと説明
    BasicID
    ID for observed and synthetic waveform This class is IMMUTABLE
    Double values will be rounded off to 3rd decimal places.
    PartialID
    ID for a partial derivative This class is IMMUTABLE
    =Contents of information for one ID=
    Name of station
    Name of network
    Horizontal position of station (latitude longitude)
    Global CMT ID
    Component (ZRT)
    Period minimum and maximum
    Start time
    Number of points
    Sampling Hz
    If one is convoluted or observed, true
    Position of a waveform for the ID
    partial type
    Location of a perturbation point: latitude, longitude, radius One ID volume:#oneIDbyte:
